      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "first",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", that a state of war was, indeed, chronic between Asa and Baasha (which way of putting need not disturb the correctness of ",
